<TEXT>
   Prices on the Tokyo Stock Exchange closed at an
all-time high Thursday, bouyed by an overnight surge on Wall
Street, and the U.S. dollar edged up slightly, traders said.
   The 225-issue Nikkei Stock Average ended the day at 28,072.02
