Club and the Canadian Club in Toronto on June 21 at the conclusion
of the summit. He said the event was not part of the summit but
``undoubtedly will deal with the conclusions and results of the
summit activities.''
   The spokesman said the two clubs are ``devoted to the flow of
ideas and the encouragement of public speakers on various national
and international issues.''
   Reagan will return to Washington following the speech.
