   3. Lotus Development Corp., Cambridge, Mass., 18.2 percent,
$395.6 million.
   4. Ashton-Tate Corp., Torrance, Calif., 16.1 percent, $267.3
million.
   5. Cincinnati Microwave Inc., Cincinnati, 15.2 percent, $80.9
million.
   6. Digital Communications Associates Inc., Alpharetta, Ga., 14.9
percent, $181.4 million.
   7. Medtronic Inc., Minneapolis, 14.7 percent, $502.0 million.
   8. Seagate Technology, Scotts Valley, Calif., 14.6 percent,
$958.1 million.
   9. Sensormatic Electronics Corp., Deerfield Beach, Fla., 14.0
percent, $98.3 million.
   10. Intel Corp., Santa Clara, Calif., 13.0 percent, $1.91
billion.
